# LeptonX Theme UI Rules

## General Style
- Clean, modern SaaS admin UI
- Inspired by LeptonX (https://x.leptontheme.com)
- Use soft shadows, rounded corners, clear spacing

## Layout
- Use container max-width: 1320px
- Use padding: 24px
- Section spacing: 24px–32px

## Cards
- Use abp-card for all sections
- Rounded corners: 10px–12px
- Shadow: subtle (not heavy)
- Header separated from body

## Colors
- Primary: blue (Lepton style)
- Background: light gray (#f5f7fb)
- Card background: white
- Border: soft gray

## Typography
- Page title: 22–26px bold
- Section title: 16–18px semi-bold
- Body text: 14–15px

## Buttons
- Primary: filled (main action)
- Secondary: outline
- Danger: red (delete)
- Use icons when possible

## Badges
- Status should use badges:
  - Published → green
  - Draft → gray
  - Pending → orange

## Icons
- Use FontAwesome or Bootstrap Icons